OL,3,C50th convict jailed after Rotherham
OL,4,Cgrooming investigation
OL,6,FA man who was the 50th person to be
OL,7,Fconvicted as part of the investigation
OL,8,Finto the Rotherham grooming scandal
OL,9,Fhas been jailed for 20 years.
OL,11,FRiyasth Hussain, 45, from Rotherham,
OL,12,Ftwice raped a girl aged about 13 in
OL,13,Fthe early 2000s and a second victim in
OL,14,Fher 20s in 2008.
OL,16,FHe was convicted of three counts of
OL,17,Frape as part of Operation Stovewood,
OL,18,Fthe National Crime Agency's largest-
OL,19,Fever investigation into historic
OL,20,Fsexual abuse.
