OL,3,C50th convict jailed after Rotherham
OL,4,Cgrooming investigation
OL,6,FThe operation examines the systematic
OL,7,Fsexual abuse of children in Rotherham
OL,8,Fbetween 1997 and 2013.
OL,10,FSheffield Crown Court heard Hussain
OL,11,Fdrove the 13-year-old to an abandoned
OL,12,Findustrial estate and raped her after
OL,13,Fstopping to offer help when she was
OL,14,Fbeing verbally abused on a street in
OL,15,FRotherham.
OL,17,FHussain abused the girl a second time
OL,18,Fafter driving to a field and raping
OL,19,Fher inside his car.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
