OL,4,Cgrooming investigation
OL,6,FProsecutor Liz Fell said: "She was
OL,7,Fliving in the care system and had been
OL,8,Fgroomed and sexually exploited by many
OL,9,Fother men, when Hussain targeted her.
OL,10,FHussain took her in his car to
OL,11,Fsecluded locations to rape her on two
OL,12,Fseparate occasions."
OL,14,FThe girl, who is now in her 30s, told
OL,15,FHussain in court: "When you met me, I
OL,16,Fwas just a fragile, vulnerable little
OL,17,Fgirl who you could easily abuse.
OL,19,F"Today, I am a woman with a voice, and
OL,20,Fmy only goal is to seek justice.
