OL,6,F"It was over 20 years ago when you
OL,7,Fstarted to rape me. 11 years ago I
OL,8,Fstarted me fight for justice, today I
OL,9,Fgot that!"
OL,11,FA second woman was raped when she was
OL,12,Fin her 20s in 2008.
OL,14,FWhile staying at a friend's home, a
OL,15,Fman that she did not know entered her
OL,16,Froom and raped her in front of a group
OL,17,Fof others.
OL,19,FThe investigators were able to
OL,20,Fidentify the stranger as Hussain.
