OL,4,Cgrooming investigation
OL,6,FIn a statement, the woman said: "My
OL,7,Fthoughts freeze whenever I think of
OL,8,Fhis name. I try not to think of him at
OL,9,Fall, but that never happens, he comes
OL,10,Finto my mind every day, this is out of
OL,11,Fmy control.
OL,13,F"I can't concentrate on my day or my
OL,14,Fthoughts and I am constantly
OL,15,Fdistracted with the living nightmare
OL,16,Fof what he did to me.
OL,18,F"My mind takes me back to when he was
OL,19,Fcontrolling me and the horrible things
OL,20,Fhe did to me. I feel so scared, even
OL,21,Fnow."
