OL,6,FSenior investigator Alan Hastings
OL,7,Fsaid: "Two survivors described with
OL,8,Fhumbling eloquence and dignity the
OL,9,Fgreat suffering that they have
OL,10,Fexperienced every day since Riyasth
OL,11,FHussain raped them.
OL,13,F"Despite the profoundly traumatic
OL,14,Fimpact of Hussain's crimes, both women
OL,15,Fremained determined to support the
OL,16,Finvestigation."
